      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with normal driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and features are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that looks great and is ready for the road.",
