    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with all major systems currently in good working order. While there are some minor cosmetic signs of wear consistent with its age, such as small surface scratches and light interior use, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. It represents a great balance of value and dependability for its next owner.",
