    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It's in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken incredible care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
