    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in showroom condition as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. All original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
